# Token efficiency

- Open every Agent task with **goal**, **definition of done**, and **out of scope** (paths/features not to touch).
- Prefer **one checklist message** over many short follow-ups; **start a new chat** when the task pivots.
- If you know the files, **name them**; avoid broad repo search unless blocked.
- Replies should be **short**: bullets, files touched, commands run—no long narrative unless asked.
- **Minimal diffs** only; no drive-by refactors or unrelated files.
- Do not `@` huge folders; paste **minimal** errors (path + small snippet). Full detail lives in `cursor.md`.
